news.title: Indore civic body seals three shops for commercial use of basements
news.para: Acting on the directives issued by collector Asheesh Singh, a joint team comprising officials from the district administration and Indore Municipal Corporation sealed the basements of four buildings that were found to be exploiting parking spaces for commercial activities.

news.title: Gaurs Group to launch its IPO in next 18 months: Manoj Gaur, CMD
news.para: ​​ Byoued by the successful launch of its luxury housing project in Ghaziabad clocking Rs 3,100 crore sales in three days, Gaur said the company has set a target to expand its business of development of housing projects across the Delhi-NCR market.

news.title: Ghaziabad: Indirapuram residents protest against pollution from dumping yard
news.para: The dumpyard, spread over 10 acres, is on a vacant land behind the Khoda police station. Residents alleged that over 100 trucks dispose of their waste at this site daily, resulting in tonnes of garbage accumulating in the yard.
